cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.SY

This paper involves machine learning and optimization techniques for autonomous driving tasks, which suggests it could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories. The most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), as the paper focuses on developing a method for policy architecture search and adaptation via gradient-free optimization. The paper also involves aspects of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), computer vision (cs.CV), and systems and control (cs.SY) as it deals with learning to drive in a simulated environment.
